    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Another solution is to use JD for OSX (<a href=\"http://java-decompiler.github.io/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">http://java-decompiler.github.io/</a>).\nFor Java 11 with BigSur version, make sure to fix a common error by adding the line export JAVA_HOME=$(/usr/libexec/java_home -v11) into the file /Applications/JD-GUI.app/Contents/MacOS/universalJavaApplicationStub.sh as suggested in <a href=\"https://github.com/java-decompiler/jd-gui/issues/332\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://github.com/java-decompiler/jd-gui/issues/332</a></p>\n"
